A REVIEW OF THE PREVIOUS UTILIZATION OF THIS TRAILER SHOWED THAT THE LAST RADIOACTIV E MATERIAL TRANSPORTED IN IT WAS A SHIPMENT OF RADIOACTIVE MATERIAL, LSA FR OM ALLIED CHEMICAL AT METROPOLIS, IL. TO RIO ALGON MINE AT MOAB, UT.  ALLIE D CHEMICAL HAS BEEN ADVISED OF THIS INCIDENT AND A COPY OF THIS ROPORT WILL BE PROVIDED TO THEM.
